title: Tech takes season series with 7-4 victory over Redhawks - Tennessee Tech
content: Tech takes season series with 7-4 victory over Redhawks  Tennessee Tech
description: COOKEVILLE, Tenn. â€“ A big inning, a huge swing, and a trio of solid pitching performances led the Tennessee Tech baseball team to an Ohio Valley Conference series-clinching victory Saturday afternoon, as the Golden Eagles (20-13, 4-5) edged Southeast Missouri, 7-4, at Quillen Field and Bush Stadium at the Averitt Express Baseball Complex.
